date.description: Date for which the analytics data is recorded.

channel_id.description: Unique identifier for the YouTube channel.

video_id.description: Unique identifier for the YouTube video.

live_or_on_demand.description: Indicates if the video was watched live or on demand.

subscribed_status.description: Indicates if the viewer is subscribed to the channel or not.

country_code.description: Two-letter country code where the data was collected.

province_code.description: Code representing the province or region where the data is collected.

views.description: Total number of views for the video.

watch_time_minutes.description: Total watch time in minutes for the video.

average_view_duration_seconds.description: Average duration of time spent watching the video in seconds.

average_view_duration_percentage.description: Average percentage of video watched by viewers.

annotation_click_through_rate.description: Percentage of viewers who clicked on annotations while watching the video.

annotation_close_rate.description: Percentage of times viewers closed annotations after they were shown.

annotation_impressions.description: Total number of times annotations were shown to viewers.

annotation_clickable_impressions.description: Number of times annotations were shown to viewers and were clickable.

annotation_closable_impressions.description: Number of times annotations were shown to viewers and were closable.

annotation_clicks.description: Total number of clicks on annotations during video playback.

annotation_closes.description: Total number of times viewers closed annotations during video playback.

card_click_rate.description: Percentage of viewers who clicked on cards while watching the video.

card_teaser_click_rate.description: Percentage of viewers who clicked on card teasers.

card_impressions.description: Total number of times cards were shown to viewers.

card_teaser_impressions.description: Total number of times card teasers were shown to viewers.

card_clicks.description: Total number of clicks on cards during video playback.

card_teaser_clicks.description: Total number of clicks on card teasers.

red_views.description: Number of views from viewers who are considered returning viewers.

red_watch_time_minutes.description: Total watch time in minutes from returning viewers.
